        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When on, prev/play/next appear as a floating overlay when you hover the album art, and the duplicate transport buttons below the art are hidden. When off, those controls stay always-visible in the transport row.",
          "target": "开启时，当您悬停在专辑封面上时，上一首/播放/下一首会作为浮动覆盖层出现，并且封面下方重复的传输按钮会被隐藏。关闭时，这些控件会始终显示在传输行中。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "How often the sidebar asks Spotify for current state. Lower = snappier, higher = fewer API calls. 3000 is a good default.",
          "target": "侧边栏向 Spotify 查询当前状态的频率。较低 = 响应更快，较高 = API 调用更少。3000 是一个不错的默认值。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Enables a lyrics toggle on the album art (hover to reveal). Lyrics fetched from lrclib.net (free, no account, community-driven LRC database). When off, the toggle is hidden.",
          "target": "在专辑封面上启用歌词切换（悬停显示）。歌词从 lrclib.net 获取（免费、无需账户、社区驱动的 LRC 数据库）。关闭时，切换按钮会被隐藏。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
